AppTargCPUEnum

Indicates the central processing unit (CPU) of the machine on which the application is running.

Name Value Description
eInvalidTargCPU 0 Invalid target CPU
eMotorola68kCPU 1 Motorola 68K
ePowerPCCPU 2 PowerPC
eIntelx86CPU 3 Intel x86
eSPARCCPU 4 SPARC
ePARISCCPU 5 PA-RISC
eMIPSCPU 6 MIPS
eAlphaCPU 7 Alpha
eArmCPU 8 ARM
eX64CPU 9 AMD/Intel x64
